      <th class="p10l"><span rel='popover' data-placement='right' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Lock a player to guarantee that they are in all generated lineups.</span>' data-original-title='Lock' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>Lock</span></th>

      <th class="align-c">Team</th>
      <th class="align-c"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Player position.</span>' data-original-title='Position' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>POS</span></th>
      <th class="align-c"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Position in the batting order.</span>' data-original-title='Batting Order' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>B/O</span></th>
      <th class="align-c basic"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Opposing team.</span>' data-original-title='Opponent' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>OPP</span></th><th class="basic sorter-input-value" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Player cost on fantasy site.</span>' data-original-title='Salary' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>SAL</span></th>
      <th class="basic sorter-input-num"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Fantasy points we project this player to score.</span>' data-original-title='Projected Fantasy Points' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>FPTS</span></th><th class="basic" style="padding:0;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Projected value. (FP/Salary)*1000</span>' data-original-title='Value' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>VAL</span></th>
      <th class="basic" style="padding:0;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Total expected fantasy points above or below projected.<br/><br/>A trend score above zero is an indicator that the player has been performing well and has favorable conditions heading into their next game.<br/><br/><i>Scroll to the bottom of the page for more information and to view the correlation between trends and fantasy production.</i></span>' data-original-title='Trend Score' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>Trend</span></th>
      <th class="basic" style="padding:0;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">The projected ownership percentage of lineups that include this player in the upcoming slate of contests.</span>' data-original-title='Projected Ownership Percentage' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>OWN%</span></th>

      <th class="align-c basic sorter-input-num" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Odds strictly on the straight-up game outcome with no consideration for a point spread.<br/><br/>More money must be risked to bet the better team; less money on the weaker team.<br/><br/>Example: The money line is -200 on Los Angeles since they have a better chance to win the game.</span>' data-original-title='Money Line Definition' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>ML</span></th>
      <th class="align-c basic sorter-input-num"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">A bet on whether the outcome of an event (usually the combined score of a sports game) will be above or below a number established in advance by the bookmaker.</span>' data-original-title='Over-Under Definition' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>O/U</span></th>
      <th class="align-c basic sorter-input-num"><span id='popover' rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">The actual total points this team is expected to score in this game.<br/><br/>Pitchers are shown as opponent runs against.</span>' data-original-title='Team Total Points' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>TM/R</span></th>
      <th class="basic" style="text-align:center;border-right:1px solid #bbb;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Game weather forecast.</span>' data-original-title='Weather' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>Weather</span></th>
      <!-- Batter vs Pitcher splits -->
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;">vs. Opp. Pitcher</th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Total games played by a player.</span>' data-original-title='Games Played' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>G/P</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Total at bats for a player within this split.</span>' data-original-title='At Bats' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>AB</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Batting average for a player within this split.<br/><br/>Calculated as (Hits / At Bats) * 100. </span>' data-original-title='Batting Average' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>AVG</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">On base percentage for a player within this split.<br/><br/>On base percentage is a measure of how often a better reaches base for any reason other than a fielding error.<br/><br/>Calculated as (Hits + Walks + Hit by Pitch) / (At bats + Walks + Hit by Pitch + Sac Flys).</span>' data-original-title='On base Percentage' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>OBP</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Slugging percentage for a player within this split.<br/><br/>Slugging percentage is a popular measure of the power of a hitter.<br/><br/>Calculated as ( (Singles) + (2 * Doubles) + (3 * Triples) + (4 * Home Runs) ) / At Bats.</span>' data-original-title='Slugging Percentage' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>SLG</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">On base plus slugging percentage for a player within this split.<br/><br/>On base plus Slugging is a measure of the ability of the player to both get on base and to hit for power.<br/><br/>Calculated as (On base percentage + Slugging percentage).</span>' data-original-title='On base plus Slugging' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>OPS</span></th>
      <th class="align-r matchup-stats-vs-pitcher hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Average fantasy points per game played.<br/><br/>Calculation: (Total Fantasy Points / Games)</span>' data-original-title='Fantasy Points per Game' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>FP/G</span></th>

      <th class="align-c pitcher-live-stats hidden"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Defined as a game in which the pitcher completes at least six innings and permits no more than three earned runs.</span>' data-original-title='Quality Start' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>QS</span></th>
      <th class="align-c pitcher-live-stats hidden"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Defined as the pitcher who last pitched prior to the half-inning when the winning team took the lead for the last time.</span>' data-original-title='Win' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>W</span></th>

      <!-- Live Optimizer: Batter stats -->
      <th class="align-c batter-live-stats hidden"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Number of times batter safely reached first base by hitting a fair ball.</span>' data-original-title='Singles' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>1B</span></th>
      <th class="align-c batter-live-stats hidden"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Number of times batter safely reached second base by hitting a fair ball.</span>' data-original-title='Doubles' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>2B</span></th>
      <th class="align-c batter-live-stats hidden"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Number of times batter safely reached third base by hitting a fair ball.</span>' data-original-title='Triples' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>3B</span></th>
      <th class="align-c batter-live-stats hidden"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">A home run is scored when a ball is hit in such a way that the batter is able to circle the bases and reach home safely in one play without any errors.</span>' data-original-title='Home Runs' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>HR</span></th>
      <th class="align-c batter-live-stats hidden"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">A base on ball (BB), also known as a walk, occurs when a batter receives four pitches that the umpire calls balls, and is then entitled to reach first base without the possibility of being called out.</span>' data-original-title='Base on Balls' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>BB</span></th>
      <th class="align-c batter-live-stats hidden"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">A run is scored when a player advances around first, second and third base and returns safely to home plate.</span>' data-original-title='Runs' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>R</span></th>
      <th class="align-c batter-live-stats hidden"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">A RBI is scored when a play allows a run to be scored without an error.</span>' data-original-title='Runs Batted In' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>RBI</span></th>
      <th class="align-c batter-live-stats hidden"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">A strikeout occurs when a batter accumulates three strikes duraing a time at bat, resulting in one out.</span>' data-original-title='Strikeouts' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>S</span></th>
      <th class="align-c batter-live-stats hidden"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">A HBP occurs when hitter is struck by a pitch. A HBP results in the batter advancing to first base.</span>' data-original-title='Hit by Pitch' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>HBP</span></th>

      <th style="text-align:center;border-left:1px solid #bbb;border-right:1px solid #bbb;padding:0;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='left' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Remove from pool of eligible players. Excluded players will not be in generated lineups.</span>' data-original-title='Exclude' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>EX</span></th>
    </tr>                        </thead>

    <h3>Optimizing Lineup...</h3>

  <div class="span47 rwo-failed hide" style="">
    <h3>We couldn't generate a valid lineup.</h3>
    <p>Here are a few possible reasons why this may have happened:</p>

    <ol>
      <li>The pool of eligible players is too small.</li>
      <li>Too many players are locked in at a position.</li>
      <li>The locked in players are expensive enough that a valid lineup is impossible.</li>
      <li>The applied filters restrict the player pool too much.</li>
      
    </ol>

    <p>Please contact support@rotowire.com if this error is still appearing after making the suggested adjustments to the player pool.</p>

    <button class="btn btn-primaryflat run-optimizer" id="rwo-error-close">Adjust The Player Pool &amp; Try Again</button>
  </div>

                              <table class="tablesorter rwo-sticky rwo-playertable" id="playerPoolTable">

    <tr>

      <th class="exclude align-c" style="border-bottom:1px solid #bbb;background:#f8f8f8;border-right:1px solid #bbb;" colspan="1">&nbsp;</th>
    </tr>

    <tr>
      <th class="p10l"><span rel='popover' data-placement='right' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Lock a player to guarantee that they are in all generated lineups.</span>' data-original-title='Lock' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>Lock</span></th>
      <th class="align-l p10l">Name</th>
      <th class="align-c">Team</th>
      <th class="align-c"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Player position.</span>' data-original-title='Position' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>POS</span></th>
      <th class="align-c"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Position in the batting order.</span>' data-original-title='Batting Order' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>B/O</span></th>
      <th class="align-c basic"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Opposing team.</span>' data-original-title='Opponent' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>OPP</span></th><th class="basic sorter-input-value" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Player cost on fantasy site.</span>' data-original-title='Salary' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>SAL</span></th>
      <th class="basic sorter-input-num"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Fantasy points we project this player to score.</span>' data-original-title='Projected Fantasy Points' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>FPTS</span></th><th class="basic" style="padding:0;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Projected value. (FP/Salary)*1000</span>' data-original-title='Value' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>VAL</span></th>
      <th class="basic" style="padding:0;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Total expected fantasy points above or below projected.<br/><br/>A trend score above zero is an indicator that the player has been performing well and has favorable conditions heading into their next game.<br/><br/><i>Scroll to the bottom of the page for more information and to view the correlation between trends and fantasy production.</i></span>' data-original-title='Trend Score' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>Trend</span></th>
      <th class="basic" style="padding:0;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">The projected ownership percentage of lineups that include this player in the upcoming slate of contests.</span>' data-original-title='Projected Ownership Percentage' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>OWN%</span></th>

      <th class="align-c basic sorter-input-num" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Odds strictly on the straight-up game outcome with no consideration for a point spread.<br/><br/>More money must be risked to bet the better team; less money on the weaker team.<br/><br/>Example: The money line is -200 on Los Angeles since they have a better chance to win the game.</span>' data-original-title='Money Line Definition' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>ML</span></th>
      <th class="align-c basic sorter-input-num"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">A bet on whether the outcome of an event (usually the combined score of a sports game) will be above or below a number established in advance by the bookmaker.</span>' data-original-title='Over-Under Definition' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>O/U</span></th>
      <th class="align-c basic sorter-input-num"><span id='popover' rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">The actual total points this team is expected to score in this game.<br/><br/>Pitchers are shown as opponent runs against.</span>' data-original-title='Team Total Points' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>TM/R</span></th>
      <th class="basic" style="text-align:center;border-right:1px solid #bbb;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Game weather forecast.</span>' data-original-title='Weather' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>Weather</span></th>
      <!-- Batter vs Pitcher splits -->
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;">vs. Opp. Pitcher</th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Total games played by a player.</span>' data-original-title='Games Played' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>G/P</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Total at bats for a player within this split.</span>' data-original-title='At Bats' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>AB</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Batting average for a player within this split.<br/><br/>Calculated as (Hits / At Bats) * 100. </span>' data-original-title='Batting Average' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>AVG</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">On base percentage for a player within this split.<br/><br/>On base percentage is a measure of how often a better reaches base for any reason other than a fielding error.<br/><br/>Calculated as (Hits + Walks + Hit by Pitch) / (At bats + Walks + Hit by Pitch + Sac Flys).</span>' data-original-title='On base Percentage' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>OBP</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Slugging percentage for a player within this split.<br/><br/>Slugging percentage is a popular measure of the power of a hitter.<br/><br/>Calculated as ( (Singles) + (2 * Doubles) + (3 * Triples) + (4 * Home Runs) ) / At Bats.</span>' data-original-title='Slugging Percentage' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>SLG</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">On base plus slugging percentage for a player within this split.<br/><br/>On base plus Slugging is a measure of the ability of the player to both get on base and to hit for power.<br/><br/>Calculated as (On base percentage + Slugging percentage).</span>' data-original-title='On base plus Slugging' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>OPS</span></th>
      <th class="align-r matchup-stats-vs-pitcher hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Average fantasy points per game played.<br/><br/>Calculation: (Total Fantasy Points / Games)</span>' data-original-title='Fantasy Points per Game' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>FP/G</span></th>

      <!-- Batter vs Pitcher Hand splits -->
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher-hand hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;">vs. Pitcher Hand</th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher-hand hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Total games played by a player.</span>' data-original-title='Games Played' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>G/P</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher-hand hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Total at bats for a player within this split.</span>' data-original-title='At Bats' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>AB</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher-hand hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Batting average for a player within this split.<br/><br/>Calculated as (Hits / At Bats) * 100. </span>' data-original-title='Batting Average' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>AVG</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher-hand hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">On base percentage for a player within this split.<br/><br/>On base percentage is a measure of how often a better reaches base for any reason other than a fielding error.<br/><br/>Calculated as (Hits + Walks + Hit by Pitch) / (At bats + Walks + Hit by Pitch + Sac Flys).</span>' data-original-title='On base Percentage' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>OBP</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher-hand hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Slugging percentage for a player within this split.<br/><br/>Slugging percentage is a popular measure of the power of a hitter.<br/><br/>Calculated as ( (Singles) + (2 * Doubles) + (3 * Triples) + (4 * Home Runs) ) / At Bats.</span>' data-original-title='Slugging Percentage' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>SLG</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-vs-pitcher-hand hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">On base plus slugging percentage for a player within this split.<br/><br/>On base plus Slugging is a measure of the ability of the player to both get on base and to hit for power.<br/><br/>Calculated as (On base percentage + Slugging percentage).</span>' data-original-title='On base plus Slugging' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>OPS</span></th>
      <th class="align-r matchup-stats-vs-pitcher-hand hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Average fantasy points per game played.<br/><br/>Calculation: (Total Fantasy Points / Games)</span>' data-original-title='Fantasy Points per Game' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>FP/G</span></th>

      <!-- Game location (Home/Away) splits -->
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-location hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;">Game Location</th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-location hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Total games played by a player.</span>' data-original-title='Games Played' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>G/P</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-location hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Total at bats for a player within this split.</span>' data-original-title='At Bats' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>AB</span></th>

      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-location hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">On base percentage for a player within this split.<br/><br/>On base percentage is a measure of how often a better reaches base for any reason other than a fielding error.<br/><br/>Calculated as (Hits + Walks + Hit by Pitch) / (At bats + Walks + Hit by Pitch + Sac Flys).</span>' data-original-title='On base Percentage' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>OBP</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-location hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">Slugging percentage for a player within this split.<br/><br/>Slugging percentage is a popular measure of the power of a hitter.<br/><br/>Calculated as ( (Singles) + (2 * Doubles) + (3 * Triples) + (4 * Home Runs) ) / At Bats.</span>' data-original-title='Slugging Percentage' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>SLG</span></th>
      <th class="align-c matchup-stats-location hidden" style="border-left:1px solid #bbb;padding-left:5px;"><span rel='popover' data-placement='bottom' data-trigger='hover' data-html='true' data-content='<span style="font-size:12px;">On base plus slugging percentage for a player within this split.<br/><br/>On base plus Slugging is a measure of the ability of the player to both get on base and to hit for power.<br/><br/>Calculated as (On base percentage + Slugging percentage).</span>' data-original-title='On base plus Slugging' style='border-bottom:1px dotted #333;'>OPS</span></th>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="span23 item" style="padding: 15px 10px;border-top:1px solid #DDD;border-bottom:none;">
          <div class="span17">
            <b>Ceiling/Upside Model</b>
            <span class="span17">
              Ceiling, or upside, is calculated by finding the average of the top FanDuel points scored, by each individual player, and weighting it based on their matchup.
                <br/><br/>
              This system is most useful for constructing <u>tournament lineups</u>.
                <br/><br/>
              <div id="applyCeilingSystem" class="btn btn-defaultflat">Use Ceiling Model</div>
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
          <div class="span24 item" style="padding: 15px 10px;border-top:1px solid #DDD;border-bottom:none;">
            <div class="span18">
              <b>Floor/Consistency Model</b>
              <span class="span17">
                Floor is calculated by finding the average of the lowest FanDuel points scored, by each individual player, and weighting it based on their matchup.
                  <br/><br/>
                This system is most useful for constructing <u>cash game lineups</u>.
                  <br/><br/>
                <div id="applyFloorSystem" class="btn btn-defaultflat">Apply Floor Model</div>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
      <div class="span23 item" style="padding: 15px 10px;border-top:1px solid #DDD;border-bottom:none;">
        <div class="span17">
          <b>Trend Model</b> <span class="badge btn-warning" style="font-size:9px;font-weight:normal;padding:0 8px;">New!</span>
          <span class="span17">
            This model adds a player's total trend value to their projection. A trend value is the expected fantasy points above or below projected. It is based on how the player has been performing and the quality of their next matchup.
              <br/><br/>
            This system is most useful for constructing <u>cash game lineups</u> with slightly more variability.
              <br/><br/>
            <div id="applyTrendSystem" class="btn btn-defaultflat">Use Trend Model</div>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>                      </div>
                      <!-- End of Projection Models -->

                      <!-- Settings -->
                      <div class="hide span47" id="settings" style="border:1px solid #DDD;overflow:hidden;">
                        
  <div class="advancedTools span47">
    <div class="span47 rwo-filter-container" style="background: #121f34;color: #ffffff;border:none;line-height: 40px;width: 100%;">
      <div class="span47 rwo-filter-left-head" style="border:none;padding: 0 10px;"><h5 class="pull-left">Optimizer Settings</h5></div>
    </div>

    <div class="span47 systemsToggle" style="padding:0;border-right:0px;">

      <div class="span23 item" style="padding: 15px 10px;border:none;">
        <div class="span17">
          <b>Reset Locked Players</b>
          <span class="span17">
            Remove the lock status from all players in the player pool.
              <br/><br/>
            <div class="btn btn-defaultflat rwo-unlock-all-players">Unlock All</div>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="span23 item" style="padding: 15px 10px;border:none;">
        <div class="span17">
          <b>Custom Projections and Salaries</b>
          <span class="span17">
            Re-apply or completely remove all customized projections and player salaries.
              <br/><br/>
            <i>Customized player data is automatically reset at the beginning of each day.</i>
              <br/><br/>
            <div id="applyCustomSystem" class="btn btn-defaultflat">Apply Customized Data</div>
            <div id="resetCustomProjSalBtn" class="offset1 btn btn-danger hidden">Reset</div>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="span23 item" style="padding: 15px 10px;border-top:1px solid #DDD;border-bottom:none;">
        <div class="span17">
          <b>Custom Players</b>
          <span class="span17">
            Remove all players added to the player pool via the "Manually Add Player" module.
              <br/><br/>
            <i>All added players will be removed at the beginning of each day.</i>
              <br/><br/>
            <div id="resetCustomPlayerBtn" class="btn btn-danger disabled">Remove Added Players</div>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>                      </div>
                      <!-- End of Settings -->
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <!-- End of Panel Navigation -->
